{"tid":1165891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逃犯條例關我撚事咩，我又唔係犯法","createTime":"2019-05-22T05:42:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T06:41:53.000Z","uid":27495,"like":15,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3d09de4b0100623c6caa8e302593df417e704c16","tid":1165891,"uid":27495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:42:47.000Z","msg":"屌，逃犯條例唔止關我事，重關我全家人事。仆街，我買咗樓冇耐，一陣啲外資走，香港百業蕭條，啲樓變哂垃圾，工又冇得做，要同大陸閪一齊食草，我重點去旅行，我重點退休，我重點生仔，好撚驚呀屌佢老母，林鄭真係戇鳩㗎，聽個雜豬頭仔玩攬炒。<br />\n<br />\n6月9日我重諗緊出唔出嚟，有女應該出。"},{"pid":"7cd374703027824ea283df705999d0823ddbfe26","tid":1165891,"uid":4917,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:45:30.000Z","msg":"D樓變曬垃圾明明係好事"},{"pid":"3c3e8838fd10181e2919650988accc024a162bb8","tid":1165891,"uid":27495,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"7cd374703027824ea283df705999d0823ddbfe26","tid":1165891,"uid":4917,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:45:30.000Z","msg":"D樓變曬垃圾明明係好事"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:46:48.000Z","msg":"你冇樓緊係咁講啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"768a46496698e13187da3c7283b892080b24b732","tid":1165891,"uid":83386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:48:57.000Z","msg":"冇樓表達關我撚事咩"},{"pid":"101ce51c8325cac6082ca0b8b8739059f3397da0","tid":1165891,"uid":27495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"768a46496698e13187da3c7283b892080b24b732","tid":1165891,"uid":83386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:48:57.000Z","msg":"冇樓表達關我撚事咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:50:36.000Z","msg":"如果你屋企唔係有錢，遲啲冇工開都幾撚慘"},{"pid":"a9db3b5af2206940ff60f6f4a48056548a0746e0","tid":1165891,"uid":27495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T05:54:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"571d8b53f2f7c43b06d